Berger Paints Nigeria Says Ganiyu Lawal Has Resigned as CEO

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-10-20T13:18:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-20/berger-paints-nigeria-says-ganiyu-lawal-has-resigned-as-ceo.html
Berger Paints Nigeria Plc (BERGER) , a
Nigerian paint-maker and marketer, said Ganiyu Lawal resigned as
chief executive officer with effect from Sept. 21.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
